    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels through a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been professionally addressed with subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains sharp with updated bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains potent, exhibiting excellent compression and linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for tactile feedback and cornering precision.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
