    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained luxury sedan that perfectly balances performance with daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, while the cabin\u2019s wood trim and electronics\u2014including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is very sound; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a clean, 'turn-key' experience for its next owner. It is a solid, honest example of a well-loved vehicle ready for many more miles.",
